edu.uab.ssg.mixomatic

Interface MixtureModel

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MixtureModel.Estimate
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEstimate, DefaultModel, LooseModel

    public interface MixtureModel
    A mix-o-matic mixture model. Implementations should model a distribution of p-values as a mixture of one uniform distribution (specified by lambda0) and one beta distribution (specified by beta distribution parameters r and s). More details are available in the paper at http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/S0167-9473(01)00046-9.
    Author:
    Jelai Wang
